{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act41side", "eventName": "輓歌燃燒殆盡", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "EA-7", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "燒燈者", "storyInfo": "為了幫故事找到結局，作家開始講述第三個故事：布莉吉與“放逐王”訂下賭約，拉芙希妮抗擊黑霧，而涅梅絲去宣告紅龍的死亡。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "stopsound", "attributes": {"channel": "read3"}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$tara_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_weaamonologue_3", "channel": "read3"}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "<i>從前有一位母親，她曾是一國的國王，卻被仇敵奪去了王冠和親人。</i>", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "<i>萬幸的是她有一位強大的女兒，她的女兒與黑林中的黑霧訂下契約，合力趕走了仇敵，女兒為母親奪回了王國，黑霧則取回了不被打攪的安寧。</i>", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "<i>母親決定為女兒舉辦一場盛大的加冕儀式，但就在儀式開始前，女兒突然死於非命。</i>", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "<i>母親萬分悲傷，繼而變得狂怒，一心想為女兒復仇，復仇的狂熱最終成為一股幾乎將整個王國燒盡的烈焰。</i>", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "<i>然而烈焰太過旺盛，驚擾了剛剛睡下的黑霧。</i>", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "<i>黑霧勒令母親安分守己，不然就要將她拖入黑暗。悲傷中的母親認定黑霧就是奪走女兒生命的東西，決定拚死一搏。</i>", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "channel": "read3"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "stopsound", "attributes": {"channel": "read3"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "59_g2_citystreets_n", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$distressed_intro", "key": "$distressed_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "涅梅絲、葦草……", "name": "布莉吉"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在城門口，遊牧民最後一次望向遠方的堡壘。"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "突然變得濃烈的燒焦味讓她想立刻拔腿就跑。她明白這代表著什麼。"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然而無論拉芙希妮是否成功，自己都應該像涅梅絲說的，立刻離開城市去找守靈人，去請他們過來，越快越好。"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "儘管涅梅絲說話時十分強硬，卻怎麼都不像是相信事情有轉機，也不像相信自己能請來守靈人。"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "刺鼻的燒焦味同樣從涅梅絲身上散發出來，讓布莉吉想起只有死者才會有的偏執。"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1690_1#1$1", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 0.5, "focus": "m", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1690_1#1$1", "afrom": 0.5, "ato": 0.5, "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還在等誰呢？等死亡摸到你的後腦杓，再和它比誰跑得快嗎？", "name": "“放逐王”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1690_1#1$1"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1690_1#1$1", "afrom": 0.5, "ato": 0.5, "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……誰？", "name": "布莉吉"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1690_1#4$1", "afrom": 0.5, "ato": 0.5, "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦，我都忘了，你能聽見我說話。", "name": "“放逐王”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1690_1#4$1"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1690_1#4$1", "afrom": 0.5, "ato": 0.5, "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我能聽見。我甚至能感受到你就在那裡……但我看不見你。", "name": "布莉吉"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1690_1#1$1", "afrom": 0.5, "ato": 0.5, "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "趕快離開這座城市吧，局外人。", "name": "“放逐王”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1690_1#1$1"}, {"id": 50, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1690_1#1$1", "afrom": 0.5, "ato": 0.5, "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聽你說的這些話，你好像也是局外人？", "name": "布莉吉"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1690_1#1$1", "afrom": 0.5, "ato": 0.5, "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然。局外人好心提醒另一個局外人，這不是天經地義的事嗎？", "name": "“放逐王”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1690_1#1$1"}, {"id": 54, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1690_1#5$1", "afrom": 0.5, "ato": 0.5, "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "布莉吉，活著。活著比什麼都重要。最遲到明天的太陽升起之前，這座城市一定會死去。", "name": "“放逐王”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1690_1#5$1"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1690_1#8$1", "afrom": 0.5, "ato": 0.5, "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聽涅梅絲的話，去找她的同族，然後跑得遠遠的，再也不要回來。", "name": "“放逐王”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1690_1#8$1"}, {"id": 58, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1690_1#8$1", "afrom": 0.5, "ato": 0.5, "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……你說得對，我該走了。", "name": "布莉吉"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我會回來。", "name": "布莉吉"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1690_1#7$1", "afrom": 0.5, "ato": 0.5, "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "回來？！", "name": "“放逐王”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1690_1#7$1"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1690_1#4$1", "afrom": 0.5, "ato": 0.5, "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈，愚蠢和倔強還真是代代相傳！", "name": "“放逐王”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1690_1#4$1"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1690_1#8$1", "afrom": 0.5, "ato": 0.5, "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她拚了命把你趕出城外，你卻要傻傻地自己跑回來？", "name": "“放逐王”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1690_1#8$1"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1690_1#8$1", "afrom": 0.5, "ato": 0.5, "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "果然，你也覺得涅梅絲只是在找個藉口讓我活下來，是嗎？", "name": "布莉吉"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1690_1#8$1", "afrom": 0.5, "ato": 0.5, "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不然呢？你以為自己能說動那些木頭腦袋？你就用手拉吧，看看明年春天會不會有一個木頭腦袋發芽了，願意跟你進入黑林！", "name": "“放逐王”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1690_1#8$1"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1690_1#8$1", "afrom": 0.5, "ato": 0.5, "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我討厭你現在說話的腔調，看不見的弟兄。", "name": "布莉吉"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1690_1#2$1", "afrom": 0.5, "ato": 0.5, "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你叫我什麼？弟兄？", "name": "“放逐王”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1690_1#2$1"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1690_1#2$1", "afrom": 0.5, "ato": 0.5, "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你身上的焦味難聞得要命，焦味之外的部分卻又和遊牧人有點像，我不知道你到底和我們有沒有關係，乾脆就這樣叫你了。", "name": "布莉吉"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1690_1#4$1", "afrom": 0.5, "ato": 0.5, "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈……哈哈哈哈哈哈！", "name": "“放逐王”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1690_1#4$1"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1690_1#11$1", "afrom": 0.5, "ato": 0.5, "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "來打個賭吧，布莉吉！", "name": "“放逐王”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1690_1#11$1"}, {"id": 81, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1690_1#11$1", "afrom": 0.5, "ato": 0.5, "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "打賭？", "name": "布莉吉"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1690_1#1$1", "afrom": 0.5, "ato": 0.5, "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "賭你離開之後，不可能在今夜，在納斯爾紗焚盡之前回來。", "name": "“放逐王”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1690_1#1$1"}, {"id": 85, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1690_1#1$1", "afrom": 0.5, "ato": 0.5, "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你要賭的明明就不是這個。", "name": "布莉吉"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1690_1#1$1", "afrom": 0.5, "ato": 0.5, "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦？那你說我賭的是什麼？", "name": "“放逐王”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1690_1#1$1"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1690_1#1$1", "afrom": 0.5, "ato": 0.5, "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你只想證明自己是對的，活下去比什麼都重要。你覺得我最終也會這麼做。", "name": "布莉吉"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是，我跟你賭。", "name": "布莉吉"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1690_1#4$1", "afrom": 0.5, "ato": 0.5, "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你還等什麼？", "name": "“放逐王”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1690_1#4$1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1690_1#4$1", "afrom": 0.5, "ato": 0.5, "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是覺得不太公平。如果你贏了，我會後悔一輩子。可要是我贏了，你也不過是看戲而已。", "name": "布莉吉"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要是我贏了，就回到你該回的地方吧，好嗎？", "name": "布莉吉"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1690_1#8$1", "afrom": 0.5, "ato": 0.5, "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "“放逐王”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1690_1#8$1"}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你覺得我該回到哪裡？", "name": "“放逐王”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1690_1#8$1"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1690_1#8$1", "afrom": 0.5, "ato": 0.5, "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不知道，但你的家肯定不在這裡。", "name": "布莉吉"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你好像被這座城市裡的人狠狠地背叛過，可是你又狠不下心去傷害他們。", "name": "布莉吉"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你裝作樂意看人自食其果的樣子，但當你剛剛說城市就要燒毀時……其實一點都不開心。", "name": "布莉吉"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是我見過最彆扭的傢伙——", "name": "布莉吉"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1690_1#6$1", "afrom": 0.5, "ato": 0.5, "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "夠了！", "name": "“放逐王”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1690_1#6$1"}, {"id": 107, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1690_1#6$1", "afrom": 0.5, "ato": 0.5, "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "布莉吉"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "59_i09", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xScaleFrom": 1.2, "yScaleFrom": 1.2, "xScaleTo": 1.0, "yScaleTo": 1.0, "duration": 35.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我答應你。要是你贏了，我該回到哪裡就回去哪裡。", "name": "“放逐王”"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但這件事是件大事，不是你傻傻地跑回來送死就能成功的。", "name": "“放逐王”"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你還需要我做什麼？", "name": "布莉吉"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "幫我向城外那幫木頭腦袋們傳個話，你就說……", "name": "“放逐王”"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（古老的廷蓋語）“已經六百多年，早就沒人怨你們了，快點去做你們應該做的。”", "name": "“放逐王”"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦，再加一句，（古老的廷蓋語）“我真是*粗口*了，一群永遠不開竅的木頭腦袋！”", "name": "“放逐王”"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊……啊？", "name": "布莉吉"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "連同那句粗口，給我向那群蠢貨一字一句地重複一遍，聽到了嗎？要不要我再罵一次？", "name": "“放逐王”"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不、不用，族中的長老偶爾會用這種語言交談，我還是聽得懂一點……", "name": "布莉吉"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那就去吧。", "name": "“放逐王”"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "布莉吉"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還在等什麼？", "name": "“放逐王”"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你跟我繞了這麼大圈，就只是在猶豫要不要把這句話告訴我，是嗎？", "name": "布莉吉"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……現在，立刻，給我跑起來！", "name": "“放逐王”"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "金髮的遊牧人深吸了一口氣，奔向城外。"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而她終究沒能看見的祖先一個人佇立在原地，久久沒有挪動一步。"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "愚蠢和倔強……", "name": "“放逐王”"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……還真是代代相傳啊。", "name": "“放逐王”"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "59_g15_castlebalcony_n", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "涅梅絲轉身離開，拉芙希妮則望向黑林。"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "太陽已經落入地平線下，宵禁即將開始。"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而她遠遠望見，比任何時候都要濃烈的黑霧，正從林中向納斯爾紗蔓延。"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "59_g2_citystreets_n", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$nervous_intro", "key": "$nervous_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#11$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呼、呼……", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#11$1"}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "趕上了……", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#11$1"}, {"id": 163, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她對著城外的黑霧舉起手中的槍，在滿城的紫色中點亮一盞明黃色的火焰。"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就好像接收到什麼訊號一樣，霧氣緩緩爬升，直至與拉芙希妮槍尖的火齊平。"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "來這裡，來溫暖的、光亮的、還有生命留存的地方……對，來這裡。", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼了？這次又要假裝我不存在嗎？", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 170, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不會讓你們如願的。", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在真正的黑暗到來之前，我絕不會熄滅這盞燈火。", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 173, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_woodcracle"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$fireburst", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.5, "r": 255.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.1, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.01, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.6, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.5}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "霧氣被她手中的火吸引，卻又無法靠近，於是順著街道流淌擴散。"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "過沒多久，當霧氣再回來時，卻已不再是她的火焰所能吸引、所能驅散的。"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "霧中有如金鐵交鳴，她突然覺得眼前的一切都一下子變暗——"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.3, "r": 1.0, "g": 1.0, "b": 1.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"name": "$eb_blacksmoke_01", "layer": 1.0}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 1.0, "g": 1.0, "b": 1.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "黑霧降臨了。"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "這就是你的答案？", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對，這就是我的答案……", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它還沒有完成，它還需要時間。", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 202, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "時間是你的敵人，而非朋友。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那也不一定。", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#3$1"}, {"id": 208, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "人們還沒有在死火中徹底淪為毫無生機或是狂暴的行屍，他們還活著，他們還來得及把火還回去。", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在涅梅絲將人們喚醒之前，你哪裡都別想去。", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 211, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "可笑……", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可笑？也許吧。", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#3$1"}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "和你相比，也許我的力量、我的智慧、我的法術的確都微不足道到可笑的地步。", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#3$1"}, {"id": 218, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我所擁有的，唯有決心。", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 220, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "59_g12_castlecorridor_n", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$distressed_intro", "key": "$distressed_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "涅梅絲一路將棺槨拖上長廊。"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "紅龍的遺骸沒有燃燒，只是靜靜躺在那裡。"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對普通人來說，死亡就該是這副樣子，但對涅梅絲而言，她甚至能聽到耳邊有縹緲的聲音正在嘲笑自己。"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "離群的守靈人沒有任何躊躇，直接將那癱軟的身體拉了起來，丟進棺槨。"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1692_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "棺槨，紅龍，你最後的歸宿……", "name": "涅梅絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1692_1#2$1"}, {"id": 240, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1692_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們這樣的人都該早早回到這樣的歸宿。", "name": "涅梅絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1692_1#7$1"}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你現在還在什麼地方用你那扭曲的笑容看著我們嗎？", "name": "涅梅絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1692_1#7$1"}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但至少這具軀殼你已經再也無法掌控了，否則你現在就該把我燒成灰燼，對不對？", "name": "涅梅絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1692_1#7$1"}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦，還有你從不離身的這把長槍……你曾從中噴出多少火焰，又害了多少個像庫林那樣的人？", "name": "涅梅絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1692_1#7$1"}, {"id": 245, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1692_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看，你自己都不知道了。", "name": "涅梅絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1692_1#2$1"}, {"id": 247, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "涅梅絲費力地舉起那把長槍，將槍尖狠狠刺進棺槨之中。"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "僅僅一瞬，火焰就從槍尖蔓延到整個棺槨，並順著用來把棺槨和涅梅絲連在一起的繩子前進蔓延，和涅梅絲自己身上的紫火融為一體。"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "幾乎致命的寒冷瞬間爬遍涅梅絲全身，但她已經很難感覺到什麼溫度了。"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1692_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "認命吧，你現在由我擺布了。", "name": "涅梅絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1692_1#2$1"}, {"id": 254, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1692_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "庫林下定的決心，沒有做完的事情，我會替他完成。", "name": "涅梅絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1692_1#7$1"}, {"id": 256, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們走吧，去那些低賤的、受蔑視的，卻在你竊取了勝利的這場戰爭中受苦的地方。", "name": "涅梅絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1692_1#7$1"}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你會被所有人看見，你的死亡會印在所有人眼中。", "name": "涅梅絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1692_1#7$1"}, {"id": 258, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們會意識到，你死了。那高傲的、不可一世的紅龍死了。愛布拉娜·都柏林就躺在這冰冷地燃燒著的棺槨之中。", "name": "涅梅絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1692_1#7$1"}, {"id": 259, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1692_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然後……他們會怎麼做呢？", "name": "涅梅絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1692_1#6$1"}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我當然希望他們能和拉芙希妮預想的一樣，在得知你的死訊之後清醒過來。", "name": "涅梅絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1692_1#6$1"}, {"id": 262, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們會知道你所代表的時日已經結束，納斯爾紗會從這場災難中死裡逃生，塔拉不必用一座城市的毀滅來慶祝自己的新生。", "name": "涅梅絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1692_1#6$1"}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是，哈哈……", "name": "涅梅絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1692_1#6$1"}, {"id": 264, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1692_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我一定是被你的火也搞得暈頭轉向了，紅龍。", "name": "涅梅絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1692_1#2$1"}, {"id": 266, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1692_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為什麼我突然覺得另一個結局……毀滅的結局……也不壞呢？", "name": "涅梅絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1692_1#8$1"}, {"id": 268, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "畢竟殺了你的另有其人，而現在……", "name": "涅梅絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1692_1#8$1"}, {"id": 269, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1692_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在才是我對你的復仇啊。", "name": "涅梅絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1692_1#2$1"}, {"id": 271, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "棺槨仍舊默然無語，涅梅絲也不再說話。"}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她沉默、癲狂而堅定地把那具燃燒的棺槨拖下樓梯，刻意讓它和每一級台階磕碰，發出不知是碰撞還是摩擦的怪聲……"}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "宛如死者乾枯的嘲弄。"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "stopsound", "attributes": {"channel": "read3"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}